Damaturu- Yobe State Governor Mai Mala Buni charged Investors and the Business community in the state to tap from the benefit of the Nexim Bank and boost investment opportunity in the state. Hajiya Husna Ibrahim, Director Information in a press statement made available to Daily Independent on Tuesday said that “The gov represented by the Secretary to the State Government (SSG) Alhaji Baba Mallam Wali at a one day sensitization workshop on export credit facility for potential investors in Yobe state organized by Yobe investment company stated that Yobe is blessed with sesame seeds and Gypsum that should be given attention and good packaging for export purposes and economic boasting.” “So doing will not only benefit direct investors but create job opportunity to the citizenry”. HOW NIGERIAN MEN CAN NOW NATURALLY STOP PREMATURE EJACULATION, LOW SPERM COUNT AND OTHER MEN'S SEXUAL NEEDS. MADAM ALWAYS WANTS IT BIGGER, STRONGER AND LONG-LASTING!!! “Government will continue to do it’s best in creating enabling environment for investors and people of the state”. “Facilitating the Nexim loan is one such gesture of Yobe government in seeing to the betterment of the Business community and boasting Income generation of the state”.